---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Should You Build Your Own Gaming PC in 2026?</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>With current hardware prices and performance, building your own gaming PC is still one of the best ways to get maximum value. Its a rewarding experience, saves you money and even gives you the skills to fix things yourself if issues arrive! Here's what you need to know.</p>

            <h2>Pros of Building Your Own PC</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Better performance per dollar</li>
                <li>Full customization and upgradability</li>
                <li>Learning experience and satisfaction</li>
                <li>Longer warranty on each individual component</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>When to Buy Prebuilt Instead</h2>
            <p>If you want convenience, warranty support (on the machine as a whole), or don’t have time to research parts.</p>

            <h2>How RigRescue Can Help</h2>
            <p>Whether you want help choosing parts, full assembly with walkthrough, or just remote advice — we’ve got you covered in Volusia and remotely.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Help Building Your PC
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
